      • neighborhoodSimilarity

        public double neighborhoodSimilarity(int paraI,
                                     int paraJ,
                                     int paraK)
        Compute the neighborhood similarity with the use of Manhattan distance. similarity = Math.exp(2 * paraK - distance(paraI, paraJ)) - 1.
        参数:
        paraI - The index of the first instance.
        paraJ - The index of the second instance.
        paraK - A value employed to compute the similarity from the distance.
        返回:
        The similarity between the two instances.
